# Drift Project Context

## What it is

**Drifter** (by Stria) is a **phase-based generative sequencer** for Ableton Live (Max for Live), plus an optional **struck-bar physical model** synth. Two playheads drift over one user-defined pattern (Reich-style); MIDI out and internal bar sound. Positioning: "Logic, not AI" — deterministic, transparent rules.

