## Conventions

- **Main patcher**: `src/drift.maxpat`; save as Live device for `drifter.amxd` (at project root)
- **Pattern file**: `src/pattern_default.txt` — format `index pitch gate` per line (e.g. `0 60 1`)
- Brand/model: Fors (fors.fm) as reference; single-word product names; minimal, confident copy
